originalText.text: Go Business Plans is a professional, attentive, accessible group. I was very pleased at how professionally and efficiently they work! Sam and Sean were the ultimate business "partners" in working on my business plan. They listened to my goals, were committed to helping me  meet my goals, offered helpful suggestions and were in constant communication with me via telephone or their online platform. It was a pleasure working with them! I recommend them and wouldn't hesitate to use their services again.

originalText.text:
Sean, Kyle and the Go Business Plan team genuinely focused on understand our secluded sub sector of the specialty food industry, which enabled them to construct a practical and reasonable business plan for my start-up.  I did not have to manage the process because they were effective and efficient project managers.

Overall they provided above and beyond services!

originalText.text: Do not use this company unless you are ready to write the entire plan yourself.  It took us over a month to get a decent draft that was still not as good as their example.   I had to submit all the market research for them.  Each revision was us rewriting it and them just sending it back to us to ask if there are any more revisions.

I can't say Thank You enough!
